reviewText:
The above-mentioned DVD lists Jennifer Saunders, Joanna Lumley, and Julie Sawalha as actors (famous for the British comedy series "Absolutely Fabulous"). However, I do not get any sense that they are at all involved with a DVD about break dancing. I would really like a clarification about the listing for this DVD. What is going on? I feel like I am being deceived. [...]
Thank you very much.
